metadata.name: Dead Generation No.1
metadata.description:
Dead Generation is a poster art-styled series based around the concept of a generation consumed by the 7 deadly sins and blinded by the new era of technology that leaves them unaware of the real world.

"More, more, more. 
The never ending quest to fill an ever growing greed.
you want it... you're intrigued.
That want turns into need.
And now you're locked into an impulse, you can't leave."
